<section class="primary-content">
  <p>It's not compulsory, but is beneficial.</p>
  <p>We are always on the look out for new members. If you want to be part of Rotherham's newest club please get in touch for details. </p>
  <p>Membership runs from January until December and costs £20 per annum +£1 admin fee charged by British Cycling.</p>
  <h2 id="whyjoin">Why join?</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>For the good times! Cycling is brilliant, but it can be even better if you're having a laugh with new friends at the same time.</li>
    <li>Ride and train with a great bunch of people, who can help you get the most out of your cycling.</li>
    <li>Lots of social events throughout the year.</li>
    <li>Being affiliated to a team means you're more likely to get entry to races as race organisers tend to offer places to members of clubs as a priority.</li>
    <li>Discounts at local shops.</li>
    <li>Our awesome kit! It's only available to club members.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2 id="whatwillireceiveformymoney">What will I receive for my money?</h2>
  <img src="<%= asset_path('template/onelifeid.jpg') %>" alt="">
  <img src="<%= asset_path('template/package.jpg') %>" alt="">
  <ul>
    <li>A <a href="http://www.giraffeuk.com/">Giraffe</a> in club colours.</li>
    <li><a href="https://www.onelifeid.com/shop/product/club-tag-id/id/CLUB_TAG_ID">OneLifeiD</a> personalised ID tags in club colours</li>
    <li>Club branded stickers</li>
    <li>A <a href="http://www.bikepure.org/">Bike Pure</a> wristband</li>
  </ul>
  <p>If you're thinking of joining, speak to someone about coming along to one of our rides and then make your mind up. We're a very friendly bunch.</p>
  <h2 id="wereabritishcyclingaffiliatedclub">We're a British Cycling Affiliated Club</h2>
  <a href="https://www.britishcycling.org.uk/club/profile/7596/sitwell-cc"><img src="<%= asset_path('template/bc-affiliate.png') %>" alt="British Cycling Affiliated Club"></a>
  <p>What that actually means is:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>We now have public liability insurance of up to &pound;10 million for our club activities</li>
    <li>You can race under our team name and gain points towards the national and regional rankings</li>
    <li>We can provide <a href="https://www.britishcycling.org.uk/clubs/membership">introductory membership discounts</a> for our club members</li>
  </ul>
  <h2 id="joinonlinenow">Join online now</h2>
  <p>Should I be accepted as a member of Sitwell Cycling Club, <strong>I agree to abide by the rules as detailed in the <a href="<%= asset_path('template/SitwellCyclingClubSitwellCCRulesandConstitution2016.pdf') %>">rules and constitution</a> and understand that participation in club activities is entirely at my own risk</strong>.</p>
  <p>Sitwell Cycling Club strongly recommends that club members have third party liability insurance. British Cycling currently have some great discounts for your first year. Have a look <a href="https://www.britishcycling.org.uk/clubs/membership">here</a>.</p>
  <p>I understand that while riding for Sitwell Cycling Club that at all times I must wear a cycling helmet.</p>
  <p><strong>Membership can be purchased from our <a href="https://www.britishcycling.org.uk/club/profile/7596/sitwell-cc#join">British Cycling</a> profile (Just look for the big red buy button) or by clicking the button below.</strong></p>
  <a href="https://www.britishcycling.org.uk/club/subscriptions/buy?club_id=7596&amp;subscription_id=1558&amp;for=me" class="button btn btn-primary">Buy membership</a>
</section>

